insert into city (id, name, country_id, description, img_url) values (1, "Tel Aviv", 1, "Nestled along the glistening shores of the Mediterranean, Tel Aviv beckons with an irresistible blend of sun-soaked beaches, vibrant culture, and boundless energy. Here, ancient history meets modern innovation in a city that pulsates with life around the clock. From the bustling markets of Jaffa to the trendy cafes of Neve Tzedek, every corner of Tel Aviv holds the promise of discovery and delight. Whether you're seeking culinary adventures, artistic inspiration, or simply a place to unwind under the sun, Tel Aviv invites you to experience the magic of its shores and embark on a journey of endless possibilities. Come, let Tel Aviv ignite your senses and leave you enchanted with its timeless allure.", "/images/cities/Tel Aviv.png");
insert into city (id, name, country_id, description, img_url) values (2, "Rome", 2, "Welcome to Rome, the eternal city where every cobblestone street whispers tales of a glorious past and every ancient ruin stands as a testament to centuries of civilization. With its rich tapestry of art, culture, and gastronomy, Rome is a timeless masterpiece waiting to be explored. From the iconic Colosseum to the majestic Vatican City, each corner of this historic metropolis offers a glimpse into the heart and soul of humanity's collective heritage. Indulge in sumptuous Italian cuisine, marvel at world-renowned works of art, and wander through enchanting piazzas where the past seamlessly intertwines with the present. Whether you're a history buff, a food enthusiast, or a romantic at heart, Rome promises to captivate your imagination and leave you spellbound with its unparalleled beauty and charm. Join us as we embark on a journey to discover the eternal allure of Rome – a city where dreams are made, and memories are forged amidst the echoes of antiquity.", "/images/cities/Rome.png");
insert into city (id, name, country_id, description, img_url) values (3, "Naples", 2, "Naples, Italy's hidden gem! Nestled in the enchanting landscapes of southern Italy, Naples beckons with its rich history, vibrant culture, and tantalizing cuisine. Explore ancient alleyways steeped in legend, savor authentic Neapolitan pizza, and soak in breathtaking views of the Tyrrhenian Sea. With its irresistible charm and warm hospitality, Naples invites you to uncover its secrets and create memories to last a lifetime. Come, experience the magic of Naples for yourself!", "/images/cities/Naples.png");
insert into city (id, name, country_id, description, img_url) values (4, "Madrid", 3, "Madrid, where history and modernity converge in a vibrant symphony of culture! From the grandeur of the Royal Palace to the lively atmosphere of Plaza Mayor, every corner of this dynamic city tells a story waiting to be explored. Indulge in culinary delights at bustling markets and tapas bars, or lose yourself in the world-class art collections of the Prado Museum. With its welcoming spirit and endless array of experiences, Madrid promises an unforgettable journey into the heart of Spain's capital. Come, discover the magic of Madrid and let its charm captivate your soul!", "/images/cities/Madrid.png");
insert into city (id, name, country_id, description, img_url) values (5, "Barcelona", 3, "Barcelona, a vibrant metropolis on the Mediterranean coast, pulses with creativity and passion. Explore the architectural wonders of Gaudí, stroll through the Gothic Quarter's labyrinthine streets, and unwind on the golden sands of Barceloneta Beach. Indulge in Catalan cuisine, vibrant nightlife, and world-class museums. Barcelona beckons with its unique blend of culture and charm, inviting you to experience its magic firsthand!", "/images/cities/Barcelona.png");
insert into city (id, name, country_id, description, img_url) values (6, "Bangkok", 4, "Bangkok, a dynamic city where ancient traditions blend seamlessly with modernity, offers a sensory feast for every traveler. Explore bustling markets brimming with exotic spices and vibrant textiles, or marvel at the gilded splendor of ornate temples like Wat Phra Kaew and Wat Arun. Indulge in mouthwatering street food delicacies, from spicy tom yum soup to savory pad Thai, before immersing yourself in the city's electrifying nightlife scene. With its bustling streets, serene river cruises, and endless opportunities for adventure, Bangkok promises an unforgettable journey into the heart of Thai culture. Come, discover the vibrant spirit of Bangkok and let its energy ignite your sense of wanderlust!", "/images/cities/Bangkok.png");
insert into city (id, name, country_id, description, img_url) values (7, "Budapest", 7, "In the heart of Europe lies Budapest, a city that effortlessly blends its rich history with modern flair. From the banks of the Danube River to the heights of Castle Hill, Budapest captivates with its stunning architecture and panoramic views. Delve into the city's vibrant cultural scene, where classical music echoes through ornate concert halls and contemporary art thrives in trendy galleries. Indulge your senses in the thermal baths that have soothed weary travelers for centuries, or sample the flavors of traditional Hungarian cuisine in bustling bistros and quaint cafes. With its timeless charm and endless opportunities for exploration, Budapest promises an unforgettable journey into the heart of Hungary. Come, discover the magic of Budapest and let its allure whisk you away on an adventure like no other!", "/images/cities/Budapest.png");
insert into city (id, name, country_id, description, img_url) values (8, "Moscow", 10, "Experience the mesmerizing blend of history, culture, and modernity in Moscow, Russia! Delve into the iconic Red Square, adorned with the majestic Kremlin and the colorful domes of St. Basil's Cathedral. Wander through the opulent halls of the historic Bolshoi Theatre or immerse yourself in the treasures of the State Tretyakov Gallery. Indulge in culinary delights at bustling markets or chic restaurants. From the vibrant nightlife to serene parks, Moscow offers something for every traveler. Come explore the heart of Russia!", "/images/cities/Moscow.png");
insert into city (id, name, country_id, description, img_url) values (9, "New York", 14, "Experience the pulsating heartbeat of the Big Apple! New York City welcomes you with its iconic skyline, Broadway lights, and bustling streets. Immerse yourself in the cultural melting pot of Times Square, where every corner tells a story. Explore the world-class museums of the MET and MoMA, or stroll through the serene oasis of Central Park. Indulge in culinary delights from gourmet food trucks to Michelin-starred restaurants. From the Statue of Liberty to the Empire State Building, every landmark is a testament to the city's enduring spirit. Discover the energy, diversity, and endless possibilities of New York City – where dreams come to life.", "/images/cities/New York.png");
insert into city (id, name, country_id, description, img_url) values (10, "Los Angeles", 14, "Welcome to the dazzling city of Los Angeles, where dreams are born and stars shine bright! Dive into the glitz and glamour of Hollywood, stroll down the Walk of Fame, and feel the magic of the entertainment capital of the world. Soak up the sun on the picturesque beaches of Santa Monica or Venice, where surfers ride the waves and palm trees sway in the breeze. Explore the cultural melting pot of Downtown LA, with its vibrant arts scene, world-class museums, and eclectic dining options. Embark on a thrilling adventure at Universal Studios Hollywood or Disneyland, where imagination knows no bounds. Indulge in gourmet cuisine, from trendy food trucks to Michelin-starred restaurants, and experience the culinary delights of a city that tantalizes every palate. With its endless sunshine, diverse landscapes, and endless possibilities, Los Angeles invites you to live your own Hollywood story. Come, discover the City of Angels!", "/images/cities/Los Angeles.png");
insert into city (id, name, country_id, description, img_url) values (11, "Cairo", 15, "Embark on an enchanting journey to Cairo, Egypt, where ancient wonders and modern marvels collide! Explore the iconic pyramids of Giza, standing as eternal guardians of the past, and unravel the mysteries of the Sphinx. Lose yourself in the bustling Khan El Khalili bazaar, a labyrinth of sights, sounds, and scents offering treasures from across the ages. Immerse yourself in the rich tapestry of Egyptian history at the Egyptian Museum, home to countless artifacts, including the dazzling treasures of Tutankhamun. Indulge in delectable Egyptian cuisine, from aromatic kebabs to sweet baklava, and experience the warmth of Egyptian hospitality. With its vibrant culture, fascinating history, and timeless allure, Cairo beckons you to uncover its treasures. Come, let Cairo cast its spell on you!", "/images/cities/Cairo.png");
insert into city (id, name, country_id, description, img_url) values (12, "Bucharest", 16, "Discover the hidden gem of Eastern Europe - Bucharest, Romania! Wander through the charming Old Town, where cobblestone streets lead to lively cafes and historic churches. Marvel at the grandeur of the Palace of Parliament, the second-largest building in the world. Dive into the city's rich cultural tapestry at the National Museum of Art or catch a performance at the Romanian Athenaeum. Indulge in traditional Romanian cuisine at local taverns or chic eateries. With its vibrant energy and captivating history, Bucharest is a must-visit destination for any traveler seeking adventure and authenticity. Come experience the magic of Bucharest!", "/images/cities/Bucharest.png");
insert into city (id, name, country_id, description, img_url) values (13, "Krakow", 17 , "Welcome to Krakow, where history and beauty intertwine. Explore the medieval charm of the Old Town, stroll through the cobblestone streets of Kazimierz, the Jewish Quarter, and pay homage at the haunting Auschwitz-Birkenau Memorial. Dive into Krakow's rich cultural tapestry at the Wawel Royal Castle and marvel at the stunning architecture of St. Mary's Basilica. Indulge in traditional Polish cuisine at quaint cafes and vibrant markets. Experience the resilience of the human spirit as you reflect on the city's Holocaust history. Krakow invites you to uncover its past and embrace its vibrant present.", "/images/cities/Krakow.png");
insert into city (id, name, country_id, description, img_url) values (14, "Lisbon", 18 , "Discover the captivating allure of Lisbon, where every cobblestone street tells a story of centuries past and every corner reveals a glimpse of modern European charm. Wander through the narrow alleys of Alfama, adorned with colorful tiles and echoing with the melancholic melodies of Fado. Marvel at the grandeur of Belém Tower and Jerónimos Monastery, testaments to Portugal's rich maritime history. Sink your toes into the golden sands of Cascais or explore the rugged coastline of Sintra. Indulge in the flavors of Portugal at bustling food markets and quaint tascas, savoring freshly caught seafood and delectable pastries. With its breathtaking views, warm hospitality, and timeless beauty, Lisbon invites you to embark on an unforgettable journey through its winding streets and sun-soaked squares.", "/images/cities/Lisbon.png");
insert into city (id, name, country_id, description, img_url) values (15, "Lagos", 18 , "Experience the sun-kissed shores and vibrant atmosphere of Lagos, Portugal! Nestled along the stunning Algarve coast, Lagos beckons with its golden beaches, crystal-clear waters, and rugged cliffs. Dive into adventure with thrilling water sports or relax on pristine sands. Explore the historic charm of the old town, where cobbled streets lead to picturesque squares and lively cafes. Discover hidden coves and sea caves on a boat tour of the dramatic coastline. Indulge in fresh seafood and traditional Portuguese cuisine at waterfront restaurants. With its blend of natural beauty, rich history, and lively culture, Lagos offers a truly unforgettable escape by the sea. Come, discover the magic of Lagos!", "/images/cities/Lagos.png");
